<div class="dst-component-card">
  <div class="flex items-baseline justify-between mb-2">
    <h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-900">Modal</h3>
    <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 font-mono">2 variants · 5 sizes · 4 states</p>
  </div>
  <p class="dst-component-intro">Centered, blocking dialog. Used for confirmations, focused tasks, content that demands attention.</p>

  <div class="dst-spec-row">
